PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1990-6/844 of May 3, 1990 (which authorized the leasing of some 141.5 hectares of land situate at Edmonton International Airport to the LEDUC TOURISM and CONVENTION ASSOCIATION for the operation of a public golf course), so as to permit the term of the lease to commence as late as January 1, 1991, one year later than now provided for.
